have certain advantages

112
00:04:39,715 --> 00:04:40,794
as well as disadvantages,

113
00:04:41,007 --> 00:04:43,976
so some companies choose to

114
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:44,657
combine two or more of them,

115
00:04:44,939 --> 00:04:46,663
in an effort to take advantage of their
respective strengths.

116
00:04:46,817 --> 00:04:48,447
For example, some companies

117
00:04:48,447 --> 00:04:50,749
